{"tid":1812987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[夕陽行業] 立法會公聽會的士司機稱收入減反問態度如何好","createTime":"2020-01-06T02:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T08:39:25.000Z","uid":277339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"649e9295b3071de4fe5e396dab0f16774a5e437b","tid":1812987,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"06.01.2020 10:32<br />\n<br />\n政府計劃以試驗形式，推出600架專營的士服務，立法會相關的條例草案委員會早上召開公聽會。有的士司機表示，近年行內生意低迷，司機收入大減，連最低工資都未必達到，<span style=\"color: red;\">經常憂心生活開支，反問「態度點會好」</span>，指若果公務員不加人工，會否對市民好。<span style=\"color: red;\">有出席市民批評，不少的士司機對乘客的態度惡劣，亦會濫收車資，</span>試過一次由旺角到元朗，有司機要價1000元。<br />\n<br />\n有車主代表則指，目前社會運動持續，的士司機與其他市民的生計均大受影響，當局如今推出起標價較高的專營的士，是不切實際，認為政府應該著力提升業界服務水平，積極打擊行內害群之馬，增加市民信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1246010&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1246010%26csid%3D261_341&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1fE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=ab16e044\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1246010&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"230dd4de2395f9928189211ad6b19de407c31831","tid":1812987,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"諗起個副meme圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d4fc30cb96919563e295b7fabb4e64e7bc57fa","tid":1812987,"uid":392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bd/Taxi_Hunter_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbd%2FTaxi_Hunter_poster.jpg&h=1360a546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3f0647d5a9a33b5af851e61bcc4c5610b975280","tid":1812987,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"報稅未